Cell["\<\
The intermediate time integral is evaluated. The integration over (t-t\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]) is performed, solving a linear equation, obtained by \
equating the coefficient of (t-t\[CloseCurlyQuote]) in the total polynomial \
to zero. In this special case, the frequency \[Digamma]  is multiplied by the \
same time interval as \[Omega].\
\>", "Text",
